CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 6, 1958, pg. A22, reads: " 'Miss Emanon" and Attendants - Shown in center is Miss Gerry Shackelford, who was chosen "Miss Emanon" of 1959 at eh Emanons' ball, Nov. 27. Her attendants were, left, Carole VeLar, and right, Barbara Alston. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, left to right: Carole VeLar, "Miss Emanon" Gerry Shackleford, and Barbara Alston, standing on exterior steps of Webster Hall
